title: Tin Foil Hat #73: Extraordinary with Henry "The Polish Starseed" Zebrowski
description:
Thank you for tuning into another spiritual episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode the boys welcome from Adult Swim's "Pretty Little Face Is Going To Hell's" Henry Zebrowski. On the episode we discuss...
1) The Last Podcast On The Left
2)The Mount Rushmore of Polish Entertainers
3) The World of Conspiracies
4)Extraordinary: The Stan Romanek Story,
5)The Siding Incident
6)Shadow People
7)Starseed: aka "Space Jesus
8) Bike Fights
9)Stan Goes To Jail
Thank you for checking out the show. We really appreciate the support.
Fun Facts: Sam Tripoli is shooting his One Hour Comedy Special at the Viper Room on March 25th at 7:30 and 9:30pm. If you would like to attend please email Sam at SamTripolilive@gmail.com.
